{"tid":96730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"在銀行吵架都能被星探挖掘？意外從路人變荷里活演員的 5 位大明星！","createTime":"2017-01-27T05:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T08:18:23.000Z","uid":9573,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd2e95d967d3985a74a12a9a555da4384f51da8","tid":96730,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"荷里活每一年都會有許多年輕的帥哥美女前往去為夢想打拼，但事實上都中能出頭成為下一代巨星的人實在寥寥可數，讓人嫉妒的是，現在我們熟悉的荷里活名演員當中，也有不少人當初只是一名路人，卻意外被星探相中，一路走向現在的一線演員之路，到底是哪一些明星擁有這樣宛如電影般的真實人生呢？<br />\n<br />\n▼莎莉&middot;賽隆（Charlize Theron）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/5879985fce344.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F5879985fce344.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=fb7c2be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看過莎莉&middot;賽隆從《女魔頭》（Monster）到《瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道》（Mad Max: Fury Road）的表演，你會認為她肯定就是天生的演員，但事實上她在年輕時一直接受著專業訓練，想要成為職業的芭蕾舞者，但卻因為膝蓋受傷不得不放棄她的舞蹈事業，讓她深陷低潮期。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/5879985eb750b.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F5879985eb750b.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=f5a62923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/587999440d066.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F587999440d066.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=85a405f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但這個低潮期卻讓她發生了人生最大的轉捩點，有一天她去銀行兌現支票時，因為員工不願意幫她換而讓她當場大發脾氣，而現場正好有一名星探發現了她的爆發力，當下就上前去詢問她想不想當演員，才短短兩天她就簽約下了第一個角色。<br />\n<br />\n▼梅爾&middot;吉勃遜（Mel Gibson）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/58799af7867ca.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F58799af7867ca.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=323c9118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年為大家帶來精彩電影《鋼鐵英雄》（Hacksaw Ridge）的梅爾&middot;吉勃遜，當初對於演員一點興趣也沒有，他是標準的「陪朋友去試鏡」，同時你可能很難想像，他在前一天才剛幹完架，因此在當天完全是鼻青臉腫，看起來一點都不帥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/58799af880025.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F58799af880025.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=1daf60c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/58799c4f3ed0f.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F58799c4f3ed0f.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=1add63ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過命運是神奇的，當時的導演剛好想找一個搞笑的角色，認為他的臉正好適合扮演一個畸形的路人，但等到兩周後他們再與梅爾&middot;吉勃遜見面時，發生他居然長得頗為英俊，因此就把他替換成主角的角色。<br />\n<br />\n▼哈里遜&middot;福特（Harrison Ford）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/58799d6b1d2af.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F58799d6b1d2af.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=99fa8106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現在已經是《星際大戰》最標誌性的人物之一，你可能很難想像哈里遜&middot;福特直到 35 歲都靠著木工維持生活，雖然期間他也演出過一些小角色，但收入完全沒辦法讓他吃飯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/58799ed8071a9.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F58799ed8071a9.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=7673e3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/58799d6c39bec.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F58799d6c39bec.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=15964ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n命運改變在《星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現》（Star Wars: Episode IV - A New Hope）開拍時，導演喬治&middot;盧卡斯（George Lucas）找他來幫忙站位，卻意外發現他實在太適合韓&middot;索羅這一個角色，同時還安排他主演另外一部經典系列《法櫃奇兵》（Raiders of the Lost Ark），從此完全改變了哈里遜&middot;福特的演員身價。"},{"pid":"c05c3d6b7e117c049e6ed63dfc9989a2440fae43","tid":96730,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:44:56.000Z","msg":"▼娜塔莉波曼（Natalie Portman）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/5879a00428316.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F5879a00428316.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=4261d363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n娜塔莉&middot;波曼從小生活在紐約長島，11 歲的她在披薩店被化妝品公司露華濃的星探相中，上前問她是否想成為模特兒？但當時娜塔莉&middot;波曼拒絕了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/5879a00544cca.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F5879a00544cca.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=ea0bc4bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年紀小小的娜塔莉&middot;波曼回答自己比較想要演戲，因此這位星探幫她推薦進電影世界，我們才能看見《終極追殺令》（L&eacute;on）中可愛的小蘿莉，讓娜塔莉&middot;波曼變成了知名的童星。<br />\n<br />\n▼鄭肯（Ken Jeong）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/5879a1eb5b257.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F5879a1eb5b257.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=266e1625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/5879a1ea572b3.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F5879a1ea572b3.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=832bf68f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61675/5879a2e954947.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61675%2F5879a2e954947.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=86c3b63e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《醉後大丈夫》中的萊斯利&middot;周（Leslie Chow）和《廢柴聯盟》中扮演的本&middot;陳（Ben Chang），都讓鄭肯大肆走紅，但你知道他原本是一位貨真價實的真實醫生嗎？2007 年他參與《好孕臨門》（Knocked Up）飾演了一名醫生，讓他決定放棄醫生工作，成為一名專職的喜劇演員。事實上在過去擔任醫生的期間，鄭肯對於喜劇就很有興趣，一邊做著單人脫口秀的相關工作，他也萬萬沒想到之後會在電影中，僅僅靠著扮演自己的性格就走紅。<br />\n<br />\n▼朱千雪（Tracy Chu）<br />\n<img src=\"http://cn.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20150826/photo/bkn-20150826144244582-0826_00862_001_02b.jpg?20150826193055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20150826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20150826144244582-0826_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20150826193055&h=207ec6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://jdailyhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/%E6%9C%B1%E5%8D%83%E9%9B%AA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjdailyhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%258D%2583%25E9%259B%25AA.jpg&h=d98f042b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪8歲時與家人移居加拿大溫哥華，擁有八級鋼琴水平，就讀西門菲莎大學。畢業後，她獨自到香港尋找工作機會，曾經當過兩年行政助理，最後決定參加2012年香港小姐競選。然而因網上投票系統伺服器發生問題，令朱千雪失落冠軍寶座，但朱千雪觀眾緣甚好，演出作品《EU超時任務》《赤道》等都叫好叫座，工作不斷，獲得多個主持及演出電視劇的機會，備受力捧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/aA5N7r.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FaA5N7r.gif&h=915e671f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04396363cf8b399589b5670f6ab76a69f70c873b","tid":96730,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"最後笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d118784d7806b73dda45e8b029437f912c0ca3","tid":96730,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:48:30.000Z","msg":"朱千雪好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641a309b2ad4a5a201693c16ee0aa31f50d5bcfa","tid":96730,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c7377a8660319aad1ff214cf42a79ac5fbcd42","tid":96730,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"發哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ee0b290003609aa726dde638d2baae9c308bb9","tid":96730,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"Ken Jeong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3acdb4b681d17aec47effa3883c097bcc4a609","tid":96730,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AB2noBL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAB2noBL.gif&h=af9b457e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c96b372ffc3fa1481ef2f1cebdd4c01d9b691430","tid":96730,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ken Jeong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd8db6402bfb889f3b434ab03388e5509517693","tid":96730,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AB2noBL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAB2noBL.gif&h=af9b457e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f566f62b8141e5216b448c76ba29429d419945e","tid":96730,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit